---
title: "Challenging Assumptions: An Empirical Analysis of Hunter Response to Chronic Wasting Disease in Alberta" 
authors:
- Pattison-Williams, J, **Xie, L**, Adamowicz, W, Pybus, M, Hubbs, A
date: "2019-09-03"
